                    <li><a href="/privacy" class="active" aria-current="page">Privacy policy</a></li>
                </ul>
            </nav>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main role="main">
        <div class="container">
            <article class="privacy-policy" aria-labelledby="privacy-title">
                <header>
                    <h2 id="privacy-title">Privacy Policy</h2>
                    <p class="last-updated" aria-label="Last updated date">Last updated: <%= new Date().toLocaleDateString() %></p>
                </header>

                <div class="policy-content" role="article">
                    <section aria-labelledby="info-collect-title">
                        <h3 id="info-collect-title">1. Information We Collect</h3>
                        <p>WisdomWell is a platform for sharing and discovering motivational quotes. We collect and store the following information:</p>
                        <ul role="list" aria-label="Types of information collected">
                            <li>Quotes submitted by users</li>
                            <li>Author names associated with quotes</li>
                            <li>Like counts for each quote</li>
                            <li>Timestamps for quote creation and updates</li>
                        </ul>
                    </section>

                    <section aria-labelledby="info-use-title">
                        <h3 id="info-use-title">2. How We Use Your Information</h3>
                        <p>The information we collect is used solely for the purpose of:</p>
                        <ul role="list" aria-label="Information usage purposes">
                            <li>Displaying quotes on our platform</li>
                            <li>Tracking quote popularity through likes</li>
                            <li>Maintaining the chronological order of quotes</li>
                        </ul>
                    </section>

                    <section aria-labelledby="data-security-title">
                        <h3 id="data-security-title">3. Data Storage and Security</h3>
                        <p>We take the following measures to protect your data:</p>
                        <ul role="list" aria-label="Security measures">
                            <li>All data is stored securely in MongoDB</li>
                            <li>We implement rate limiting to prevent abuse</li>
                            <li>Input validation and sanitization for all submissions</li>
                            <li>Regular security updates and monitoring</li>
                        </ul>
                    </section>

                    <section aria-labelledby="no-collect-title">
                        <h3 id="no-collect-title">4. What We Don't Collect</h3>
                        <p>We do not collect or store:</p>
                        <ul role="list" aria-label="Information not collected">
                            <li>Personal identifying information</li>
                            <li>Email addresses</li>
                            <li>IP addresses (except for rate limiting)</li>
                            <li>Cookies or tracking data</li>
                        </ul>
                    </section>

                    <section aria-labelledby="user-rights-title">
                        <h3 id="user-rights-title">5. Your Rights</h3>
                        <p>You have the right to:</p>
                        <ul role="list" aria-label="User rights">
                            <li>Submit quotes anonymously</li>
                            <li>Edit or delete your submitted quotes</li>
                            <li>Like or unlike quotes</li>
                        </ul>
                    </section>

                    <section aria-labelledby="third-party-title">
                        <h3 id="third-party-title">6. Third-Party Services</h3>
                        <p>We use the following third-party services:</p>
                        <ul role="list" aria-label="Third-party services used">
                            <li>MongoDB for data storage</li>
                            <li>Font Awesome for icons</li>
                            <li>Google Fonts for typography</li>
                        </ul>
                    </section>

                    <section aria-labelledby="policy-changes-title">
                        <h3 id="policy-changes-title">7. Changes to This Policy</h3>
                        <p>We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Any changes will be reflected in the "Last updated" date at the top of this page.</p>
                    </section>

                    <section aria-labelledby="contact-title">
                        <h3 id="contact-title">8. Contact</h3>
                        <p>If you have any questions about this privacy policy, please contact us through our <a href="https://github.com/boobeh123/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-label="Contact through GitHub repository">GitHub repository</a>.</p>
                    </section>
                </div>
